title: Limewire Pro 4.18.2 [limewirepro.it.tt]
description:
As always: Absolutely no viruses or any other kind of malware included. The file was checked at VirusTotal.com with more than 30 engines. This is the latest Beta release (as of 6-Jun-2008) of LimeWire.

Description of LimeWire:
LimeWire is a file sharing program running on the Gnutella Network. It is open standard software running on an open protocol, free for the public to use. LimeWire allows you to share any file such as.mp3s, .avis, jpgs, tiffs, etc. Limewire is written in Java, and will run on Windows, Macintosh, Linux, Sun, and other computing platforms. Publish your original content to the world without setting up a website!

Changelog: http://wiki.limewire.org/?title=Changelog

Note: If you want to download the file at high speed with your browser, visit http://limewirepro.it.tt
